ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectCPFTA Rules of Origin for Casual Goods Regulations
PrecisCanada-Peru Free Trade Agreement Rules of Origin for Casual Goods Regulations (CPFTA) set out the origin requirements for low-value shipments and for goods imported by travelers to ensure that eligible goods qualify without onerous documentation requirements.
